msgstr "W panelu :guilabel:`Utwórz klucz API` wprowadź :guilabel:`Nazwę`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/address_autocomplete.rst:74
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Select API restrictions` dropdown, specify which APIs the "
